To-Do List Application (Tkinter)
A simple and user-friendly To-Do List application built using Python's Tkinter library. This app allows users to add, remove, and manage daily tasks with ease.

Features
 Add new tasks
 Remove selected task
 Delete all tasks with confirmation
 Warning messages for invalid actions
 Exit the application

How It Works
Enter a task in the input field.
Click "Add Task" to add it to the list.
Select a task and click "Remove Selected Task" to delete it.
Click "Delete All Tasks" to clear the entire list.
Click "Exit" to close the application.

